com.google.appinventor.client.widgets.properties
Class EditableProperty

java.lang.Object
  com.google.appinventor.client.properties.Property
      com.google.appinventor.client.widgets.properties.EditableProperty

public final class EditableProperty
extends Property

Property for display in a PropertiesPanel.

Such properties have an associated PropertyEditor, hence the name of this class.
